items.sentence: Tom asked me which university I wanted to go to.
Tom stayed hidden in the closet for a long time.
Tom returned to Boston to live with his parents.
Tom asked me how much homework I still had left.
Tom asked me if I could help him clean his room.
Tom didn't tell his parents about what happened.
Did you notice that Tom was wearing a new shirt?
Tom still hasn't eaten the cookies you gave him.
By the time Tom gets here, I'll already be gone.
I wonder how much Tom knows about what happened.
